card_text: If you control "Jinzo": Target 1 card on the field; destroy it, then, if it was a Trap, you can apply 1 of these effects.$N●Negate the effects of 1 face-up card on the field until the end of this turn.$N●All "Jinzo" you control gain 800 ATK.$NYou can only activate 1 "Cyber Energy Shock" per turn.
